OL,3,CReform's latest migrant policy makes
OL,4,Cbold claims but detail is scarce
OL,6,FNevertheless, their lead in the
OL,7,Fopinion polls gives them enough leeway
OL,8,Fto exert considerable pressure on both
OL,9,Fthe government and the opposition.
OL,11,FUnder their proposal, people with
OL,12,Fsettled status would be required to
OL,13,Freapply for a visa every five years.
OL,14,FThe conditions would be tougher than
OL,15,Ftoday: a higher salary threshold and
OL,16,Fno access to benefits or free NHS care.
OL,18,FFor those who fail to qualify, the
OL,19,Frisk would be stark - potential
OL,20,Fdeportation.
