OL,6,F"None of them will be given indefinite
OL,7,Fleave to remain," said Farage of those
OL,8,Fmigrants who came to the UK under
OL,9,Fformer PM Boris Johnson's tenure, in
OL,10,Fwhat the Reform leader termed the
OL,11,F"Boriswave".
