OL,3,CReform's latest migrant policy makes
OL,4,Cbold claims but detail is scarce
OL,6,FILR is currently the main route to
OL,7,Fcitizenship, with tens of thousands of
OL,8,Fpeople using it to secure British
OL,9,Fcitizenship. Barring EU citizens with
OL,10,Fsettled status, Reform's plan would
OL,11,Fretroactively apply new rules to those
OL,12,Falready living in the UK, meaning that
OL,13,Ffamilies established in Britain for
OL,14,Fyears could see their status stripped
OL,15,Faway. That prospect alone makes legal
OL,16,Fchallenges almost inevitable, which
OL,17,Fwould quickly become a stumbling block.
