OL,3,CReform's latest migrant policy makes
OL,4,Cbold claims but detail is scarce
OL,6,FUltimately, though, Farage's framing
OL,7,Fof the issue is telling. While most
OL,8,Feconomists argue that migrants on
OL,9,Faverage wages are net contributors to
OL,10,Fpublic finances, Farage argues the
OL,11,Fopposite. It's a deliberate pitch
OL,12,Fagainst the consensus view and a clear
OL,13,Fattempt to carve out political ground
OL,14,Fto the right of the Conservatives.
OL,16,FFarage is making it clear that Reform,
OL,17,Fin their promises at least, will go
OL,18,Ffurther than any other party when it
OL,19,Fcomes to immigration.
