OL,6,FWhat the policy would certainly mean,
OL,7,Fif ever implemented, is a programme of
OL,8,Fmass deportations on a scale unseen in
OL,9,Frecent British history. Farage, much
OL,10,Flike President Trump, knows how to
OL,11,Fgenerate a headline, even if the
OL,12,Fsubstance and details are still being
OL,13,Fworked out, and while he's ahead in
OL,14,Fthe polls, the current Reform strategy
OL,15,Fis unlikely to change.
